Starting with a round center of amber colored glass, the color gets darker then gradually as you go out to the outer ring of the disc, it is a light amber color, that almost looks as if it were glowing. The sculpture comes with a black adjustable stand that will allow a variety of positions for different uses and occasions. This glass disc and stand will would be gorgeous on an entryway stand or a window where the light will add even more character to the piece.

The Crestview Collection Anchor Statues come in a set of two and are made from aluminum with a silver finish. They are made in the traditional shape of ship anchors and are mounted on medium brown finished wood. These statues will add beauty to your coastal style home decor or included in a special display for your favorite sailor, Navy or Marine service person. These statues would make a perfect retirement gift for your boating enthusiast.

The Crestview Collection Lloyd Spheres, Set of Three are made of ceramic glass and have a high gloss finish. The medium blue and indigo marbling give each sphere the look of a new planet in creation. Because the process of putting colors on ceramics before firing is so unique, no two will be exactly alike. Display these spheres as a set or place them around your room to bring the space together.

Product Title: miramar tall umber blown glass disc with stand
Description: The Crestview Collection Miramar Tall Umber Blown Glass Disc with Stand looks like you have captured an eclipse and brought it into your home. The deep-brown color of umber gradually gets lighter on the outside of the disc. The sculpture comes with a black adjustable stand that will allow a variety of positions for different uses and occasions. This disc and stand stands a total of 22-inches tall and will add beauty and intrigue to your transitional home decor.

The Crestview Collection Relic Statue looks like you have acquired a piece of an ancient ruins. It is made from cement and the 9-inch x 4-inch base is a solid piece of cement with two rods extending up to hold the decorative square, lacey, floral designed block. A perfect reminder of travels to Europe or even to the cathedrals of the east. The overall height of this statue is 12.5-inches.

The Crestview Collection Running Free Statue depicts three horses as they gallop over the land, the wind catching their manes, their expressions are of graceful effort. Carved from wood, this horse statue stands a full 17.5-inches high and is 23-inches long. The brown finish has been carefully rubbed to highlight the features of the horses that join onto a rectangular base made of wood that has been stained to match the lighter part of the horses and then set on a base with four legs that is the color of the darker highlights on the horses. This statue will add beauty to a den, library, bedroom, or any other room where your equestrian lover likes to be to let their mind run away with the free run of the statue.

The Crestview Collection Windy Woods Tree Sculptures come in a set of two and are made from durable metal. The roots of the trees cling to the ground as the tops of the leafless trees are bent and blown to their very limit. This sculpture is a true depiction of one of the strongest forces of nature and the strength of the roots of the tree. These sculptures will add interest to your rustic home decor.

The Crestview Collection Phoenix Large Curled Sculpture is made with aluminum and has a multi-colored finish. The base of the sculpture is a dark brown, then it goes to a lighter brown, metallic finish and then is topped with a light metallic finish almost as it had been submerged in a liquid and where it sat in the liquid the longest is the darkest color. Small feet are placed on the bottom to keep the 20-inch high piece stable. The curvatures of this sculpture are pleasing and will be ideal for your modern style home decor.

The Crestview Collection Blythe Large Sculpture II features a single, light bronze, leaf that juts from the top of a white, marble base. This sculpture is 26.5-inches tall. Finely detailed, this sculpture adds beauty simply, yet boldly to your transitional home decor.

Product Title: cacti succulent sculptures on marble base

Description: The Crestview Collection Momma Bear Statue is made of a sturdy resin material with a brown finish that has been molded to look like carved wood. If you look at the momma bear, she looks so proud of what her cubs are doing, she holds her heart with joy. Perfect for a den, man cave, night stand, accent table, or country cabin, this statue is a must have for bear and nature lovers.

Product Title: large oasis hand finished metal cactus
Description: The Crestview Collection Large Oasis Hand Finished Metal Cactus is 24-inches tall and is "planted" in a round dark brown planter that is highlighted with a touch of a golden rim. Each leaf of the succulent has been hand finished and feature a serrated edge, a brown finish that has been dotted with a metallic finish showing through on the underside and just the opposite on the inside of the leaves. The detail given to each leaf is outstanding and this sculpture will add beauty to your collection.

The Crestview Collection Elliot Large Sculpture II is crafted from aluminum and has a bright, silver finish. The open leaf design ignites the mind as you can see it as it is, or allow your imagination to fill it with the colors of the season. This sculpture stands 24.5-inches high and sits on a white marble base.

The Crestview Collection Horse Walker Statue is made from cast aluminum and has a silver and steel finish. The artist has gracefully added the sway of the back, the head with perked up ears, and the legs that are prancing along. The statue stands 15-inches high and is secured to a rectangular base adding to its stability. Perfect for the equestrian in your home, this statue will look beautiful in any room of your home.

Product Title: large oasis hand finished palm tree
Description: The Crestview Collection Large Oasis Hand Finished Palm Tree stands 30-inches tall and is crafted from metal and then given a black finish. A touch of gold shows on the edges of the individual leaves and around the top of the square pot it is "planted" in. This sculpture is detailed right down to the black rocks that surround the ringed trunk of the tree that leads upward to the palms. This statue will add a tropical flare to your rustic style home decor.

The Crestview Collection Fauna Sculpture features a single banana tree leaf made with aluminum and with a pleasant green finish. This 51-inch tall sculpture brings a tropical feeling into your coastal style of home decor -- you can almost feel the warm trade winds blowing.

The Crestview Collection Medium Black Statue is a reindeer. It has a brown and bronze finish which illuminates as it is shined by light. Made out of aluminum metal this traditional style statue is a great touch to your home paired next to something that will warm up your room. The details of this medium statue are swift and subtle showing what you can put it with to make it the perfect space.

The Crestview Collection Elliot Medium Sculpture III is crafted from aluminum and has a bright, silver finish at the bottom of the leaf and a bright, gold finish at the top of the leaf. The open leaf design ignites the mind as you can see it as it is, or allow your imagination to fill it with the colors of the season. This sculpture stands 19.5-inches high and sits on a dark gray marble base.

Product Title: medium oasis hand finished metal cactus
Description: The Crestview Collection Medium Oasis Hand Finished Metal Cactus is 16-inches tall and is "planted" in a round dark brown planter that is highlighted with a touch of a golden rim. Each leaf of the succulent has been hand finished and feature a serrated edge, a brown finish that has been dotted with a metallic finish showing through on the underside and just the opposite on the inside of the leaves. The detail given to each leaf is outstanding and this sculpture will add beauty to your collection.

The Crestview Collection Dixie Sculpture is made of aluminum with a brown finish and stand an impressive 15.5-inches tall. It will give you a happy "Cock-a-doodle-do" greeting every time you look at him. This rooster has been sculpted with great detail from the top of his head to the nails on his claws. This sculpture will add character and charm to a breakfast nook, country kitchen or dining room.

Product Title: small oasis hand finished metal cactus
Description: The Crestview Collection Small Oasis Hand Finished Metal Cactus is 14-inches tall and is "planted" in a round dark brown planter that is highlighted with a touch of a golden rim. Each leaf of the succulent has been hand finished and feature a serrated edge, a brown finish that has been dotted with a metallic finish showing through on the underside and just the opposite on the inside of the leaves. The detail given to each leaf is outstanding and this sculpture will add beauty to your collection.

The Crestview Collection Water Pails come in a set of two and are made with metal and a fine layer of gray cement to give them an antique look and feel. The handle on the pails are black metal and are positioned to give balance to each pail. These pails would look beautiful filled with flowers and set out for display and with their neutral color and old style; sunflowers in the fall would add to your rustic style home decor.

The Crestview Collection Phoenix Medium Curled Sculpture is made with aluminum and has a multi-colored finish. The base of the sculpture is a dark brown, then it goes to a lighter brown, metallic finish and then is topped with a light metallic finish almost as it had been submerged in a liquid and where it sat in the liquid the longest is the darkest color. Small feet are placed on the bottom to keep the 16.5-inch high piece stable. The curvatures of this sculpture are pleasing and will be ideal for your modern style home decor.

Organize your bookshelf with The Crestview Collection A To Z Bookend Pair. Featuring the letters A and Z with tones of black and gray, this stylish and sturdy resin based bookend set will hold your collection, and add to your decor at the same time.

The Crestview Collection Lazy Days Statue has a loveable brown bear that has decided to lay down for an afternoon nap. Made of sturdy resin, this bear will quickly charm his way into your heart. Ideal for a den, man cave, night stand, or accent table, this statue will remind you to put your feet up and stay a while.

The Crestview Collection Dove Statues are made from durable resin with a cream colored, stonelike, finish and come as a set of two differing birds. Doves are the symbol of peace and harmony and will be a welcome addition to any room where you want to capture these feelings. These dove statues are sized to be similar to a real dove.

The Crestview Collection Dani Blown Glass Bowls, Set of Two shimmer with a beautiful brass finish and like most blown glass, each piece takes on characteristics of its own. The bowls come in two different sizes -- the large one is 10.5-inches in diameter and the small bowl is 6.5-inches in diameter. These bowls will look lovely as a display piece, or sitting close-at-hand on a table with your favorite wrapped candy.

The Crestview Collection Valentina Covered Vases are made from textured glass and have a natural earth tone, graduated stone look going from dark gray to gold and then to light gray as you move up the bottle. Each of the set of two, is topped with a circle, brass colored stopper that is the same on both and they are crafted from aluminum. These vases are ideal for your traditional style home decor.

The Crestview Collection Tegan Vase comes in a set of two in different sizes, both having the same white finish. The vases are finely ribbed from top to bottom. Each rib is the same size as the next giving it an almost smooth appearance from far away and a pleasing symmetrical look close up. The neck of this vase is narrow and will look enchanting with a small display of flowers. Both vases are tall enough that they could be placed on the floor or in a room with high ceiling and still be noticed.

The Crestview Collection Willow Gold Larger Pierced Bowl is made from cast aluminum and has been given a rustic brass finish. There are openings in the bowl that look as though pieces were ripped out of it and a dark vein of color swirls its way around the bowl's inside and ever so slightly spills to the outside. This bowl will attract attention on its own or included in a display.

The Crestview Collection Tinsdale Vases are made of ceramic and come in a set of two in a silver and steel finish. The small, round vase measures 12.6-inches tall and the large oval vase stands 17.72-inches tall, giving you a pleasing effect in your display. The silver bases have small strips of material that has been randomly placed to give an abstract weave. Each vase has a stopper in the top that is identical to the other. These vases will complement your transitional or modern style home decor.

The Crestview Collection Quiver Vases are cream colored tubes, detailed with a black feather pattern that encircles both vases in this set. The vases are made of ceramics and will be ideal for floral arrangements or how about some peacock feathers. Another use for these vases would be in the kitchen to hold your cooking utensils -- with one taller and one shorter, you will have a place for everything.

The Crestview Collection Willow Gold Medium Pierced Bowl is made from cast aluminum and has been given a rustic brass finish. There are openings in the bowl that look as though pieces were ripped out of it and a dark vein of color swirls its way around the bowl both inside and outside. This bowl will attract attention on its own or included in a display.

The Crestview Collection Suri Sculpted Bowl is crafted from aluminum. The inside of the bowl is a shiny brass finish, while the outside is a darker bronze finish. This bowl will add dimension to any table you place it on and its deep curve will be ideal for displaying fresh fruits or nuts or simply as a display piece in your transitional home decor.

The Crestview Collection Zen Japanese Inspired Bottles are basic shapes and colors of white, gray, and black for simplicity. Being in a state of Zen, means being at peace with your own thoughts and being aware of your place in the universe -- to reach ultimate enlightenment. These ceramic bottles placed in an appropriate place in your home or office, will give you a focal point to concentrate on to consider the mysteries of the universe -- perfect for your transitional style of home decor.

The Crestview Collection Thoreau Large Lidded Jar features a bright brass finish that brings sparkle to your home. Made of glass, this jar has a transitional style that will blend with any decor. Place this large jar on any table or shelf for the perfect accent piece.

Product Title: medium morrow urn with branch handle
Description: The Crestview Collection Medium Morrow Urn with Branch Handle will look stunning on any table or bookshelf. Made of metal, this urn features a brown finish on the body. A silver-finished handle resembles a tree branch. Accent your home with this transitional style urn.

The Crestview Collection Caron Large Water Bottle is a beautiful decorative pitcher that will bring a rustic style to your home. This ceramic bottle has a cream finish. Standing tall and narrow, this pitcher has a decorative handle wrapped in wire.

The Crestview Collection Isla Bottles & Tray is a beautiful display piece with three ceramic jars that sit securely on the whitewashed tray. The bottles are different sizes and shapes and when put together are very pleasing to the eye. To blend with the tray, the bottles have also been given a white, aged finish on the outside and the inside is painted to look like natural terracotta.

Product Title: large morrow urn with branch handle
Description: The Crestview Collection Large Morrow Urn with Branch Handle will be a stunning accent piece in your home. Placed on a bookshelf or table, this decorative urn has a brown finish on the metal construction. A handle at the top resembles a tree branch with a silver finish. This large urn has a transitional style that will blend with any decor.

The Crestview Collection Geometrical Farmhouse Vases includes two vases of different sizes. Both vases are made of ceramic with a white finish. Black details create a geometrical design and complement the black band around the lid. Each lid features a diamond-shaped handle. These traditional-style vases add a charming element to your home decor.

The Crestview Collection La Palata Vases come in a set of two and have been made from textured cement. They have a gray and black stippled finish that gives them a very neutral presence in your room. These vases would look beautiful with floral arrangements in them to add color to your room.

The Crestview Collection Caron Medium Water Bottle will look beautiful perched on a table or shelf. Made of ceramic, this decorative pitcher has a cream finish. The handle is wrapped in cream wiring. The speckled finish on the body of the pitcher enhances the rustic style.

The Crestview Collection Isla Cane Wrapping Bowls are made from terracotta clay and come in a set of three different sizes and shapes. Two of the pieces are shaped in an urn style while the third piece is an open bowl. The two urn style pieces have been painted with cream colored paint and have a tan wrapped pottery ridge along the top. The open bowl has been painted with the cream colored finish both inside and outside but has the same tan, wrapped look around the top. To add interest, holes have been punched through the pieces just under the rims and then a thin strand of cane has been wrapped through the holes and look like they are holding on the tan rims. These bowls would look charming on a table in a coastal or rustic style setting.

The Crestview Collection Bar Harbour Bottle Green Glass with Cane Wrapping Candleholder comes in a set of three with varying shapes and heights. With just a hint of green in the glass, these pieces add color to your decor in a soft tone making the natural tan color of the cane wrapping the highlight of the piece. Use these candleholders as a centerpiece on a table in your transitional style home decor.

The Crestview Collection Large Rowan Vase is the ideal home for any bouquet of flowers. This glass vase features a multi-color finish with hues of white, green and gold blending together. This tall, narrow vase has a cylindrical design with a gold band around the top. This transitional style vase makes the perfect accent piece for any home.

The Crestview Collection Beacon Cylinder Vases come in a set of three in varied heights. The ceramics have been finished with bright gold and then looks frosted with gray at the top and as you come down the vase it looks like the frost has been scrapped off in straight lines both vertically and horizontally, to reveal the gold. These vases will be great for floral arrangements or on their own on a console in an entryway.

The Crestview Collection Patton Bowls are made of aluminum and have a bright golden finish on the inside and a dark brown finish on the outside of the two pieces in this set. Each piece is a different size giving you multiple ways to use these bowls. The edges of the bowls rise and fall around the circumference of the bowl with one peak rising above the others. These bowls will add to your modern style home decor.

The Crestview Collection Large Journey Planter is made of metal that has been tempered to bring out a beautiful finish of steel, bronze, and blues that all shimmer and reflect light. The 14-inch opening and 11-inch depth will allow you to plant a fairly large upright plant so the beauty of the planter can always be seen.

The Crestview Collection Monterey Medium Vase is made of terracotta and features a distressed gray and brown finish. Decorative spirals around the outside give this rustic style vase a charming look. This medium-size vase is the perfect place to display a stunning bouquet of flowers.

Product Title: cannes medium glass bottle with round ball stopper
Description: The Crestview Collection Cannes Medium Glass bottle with Round Ball Stopper features a bell-shaped design. This stunning bottle is made of glass with a green, silver and tan finish throughout the piece. A round ball stopper sits atop the bottle. This transitional-style bottle makes the perfect decorative piece for your home.

Crestview Collection introduces our Akoya Pearl Jars, a true piece of art that exudes timeless elegance and sophistication. Crafted with the utmost attention to detail, these jars boast a unique cream and blue color palette made from iridescent pearlized glass that lends a touch of ethereal beauty to any room. Its organic waved texture gives it a natural, almost handmade feel. The shiny metal top with an agate stone house in a silver ring adds a touch of luxe, elevating this accessory to statement piece status.

Product Title: cadence small bottle with ball stopper
Description: The Crestview Collection Cadence Small Bottle with Ball Stopper has a simple, delicate design that will look perfect on any table or shelf. A soft cream finish on the bottle matches the round ball stopper. This transitional-style bottle is made of glass and features sharper edges than a soft round bottle.

The Crestview Collection Lark Bowls Set is made from aluminum and has been given a rich bronze finish. The bowls are two different sizes and both feature the same strong design. The metal shows details as well as flaws that naturally happen as you work with metal. These bowls will look beautiful in a transitional style decor.

The Crestview Collection Ikat Hand painted Planters come in a set of two and have a look of a woven blanket with two shades of blue, grey, and cream colored paint on a ceramic tray. The planter baskets are made of ceramic and can be used to store items like linens or as a planter. Each planter has convenient handles on the two sides to make lifting them easier. These planters will add beauty to your rustic style home decor.

Product Title: small esme bottle with wrapped agate accents
Description: The Crestview Collection Small Esme Bottle with Wrapped Agate Accents is a small but stunning decorative piece. The bottle resembles a pillow cushion shape with a gold-green finish. A multi-colored agate stone handle adorns the top of the bottle. This transitional, glass bottle is the perfect accent piece for any home decor style.

The Crestview Collection Birds Nest Statue features two delicate birds standing on the edge of their nest. Featuring tones of white and cream, this statue measures 7-inches x 7-inches x 5-inches. Delight the bird lover in your home with this lovely and elegant statue.

The Crestview Collection Hilliard Medium Lidded Jar is crafted from aluminum. The ball and lid of the piece has been finished with an aged, tarnished silver look and the handle on the lid has a bright shiny brass finish. The contrast in the two metal colors adds beauty and interest to this jar. Use this jar on an accent table or as a centerpiece on larger table or console.

The Crestview Collection Mailie Vase Set includes two vases of different sizes. Each vase features a glass flute with a bronze finish. The flutes sit within aluminum cups with a brown finish that resemble twigs. The traditional yet rustic style of these vases makes them the perfect home for flowers among any decor style.

The Crestview Collection St. Germaine Double Glazed Ceramic, Matte and High Gloss Vases come as a set of three, each with a different shape. The vases are ceramic glass and the bottom section of each has been given a shiny finish that highlights its color, while the tops of the vases have a matte finish in the same shade of green. These vases will look beautiful with a small floral arrangement, grouped together as a centerpiece on a table, or separated throughout a room to bring your traditional style home or office decorating, harmony throughout.

The Crestview Collection Taos Medium Carved Square Vase has an eye-catching rustic style. Decorated with etched geometric patterns, this vase is the perfect accent piece for your home. This square-shaped vase creates a beautiful home for a bouquet of flowers. The brown and black finish of this vase provides a neutral coloring that will blend into your existing decor.

Experience sculptural beauty with the Crestview Collection Fenwick Vases. This set of three vases features distinct sculpted shapes crafted from matte white ceramic. Perfect for adding a touch of modern elegance and artistic flair to any space in your home.

Enhance your space with the cool and contemporary Crestview Collection Braxton Vases. This set of two ovoid-shaped vases features a striking contrast between matte black and tan finishes. Perfect for adding a touch of modern sophistication to any room in your home.

The Crestview Collection Medium Kai Vase combines gray, black and gold hues to give you an earthy feel. A smooth glass construction at the top of the piece complements the textured bottom half to present a balanced vase that will look beautiful with your favorite flowers. Complete your home with this transitional style vase on any table or shelf.

Product Title: cannes large glass bottle with round ball stopper
Description: The Crestview Collection Cannes Large Glass Bottle with Round Ball Stopper is made of glass with a striking green, silver and tan finish. This genie bottle-shaped decorative piece will look beautiful on any table or shelf. A round ball stopper completes this accent piece. Add this transitional-style bottle to your home for a beautiful finishing touch.

Accentuate your decor with the Crestview Collection Ellington Vases. This set of two features embossed metal with  a washed taupe hand finish and a slender profile, adding understated elegance to any space. Versatile and chic, they are perfect for sophisticated greenery or as standalone decorative pieces.

The Crestview Collection Austin Medium Hand Painted Bottle has a sturdy terracotta construction. A brown background shows off the hand-painted black flower design. This jug-shaped bottle has a narrow neck, making it the perfect home for beautiful flowers. Add this rustic bottle to your home as stunning accent piece.

The Ashwell Medium Lidded Vase by The Crestview Collection goes well with the Ashwell Large Lidded vase and the Ashwell Table Lamp, also by The Crestview Collection. With dimensions of 11.8-inches x 14.5-inches, this lamp's warm rustic brass finish gives beautiful traditional style to your decor.

The Crestview Collection Glass Vase set includes three vases, small, medium and large. Made of glass, these vases have a transitional style that allows them to blend with any decor. These vases have an octagonal design that gives them a geometric look. Add these three vases with a brass finish to your home.

The Crestview Collection Mila Large Urn has a transparent, smoked tulip glass jar with gray aluminum on the round base as well as the round lid. The lid features bare branches extending above the jar to a height of 20.5-inches. This urn will look beautiful on an accent table, end table, console, or as a centerpiece in your traditional style home decor.

The Crestview Collection Annalisa Covered Vases come in a set of two; one is taller and more slender than the other adding dimension and eye appeal. The vase is made of glass and it has a iridescent, silver finish on the textured glass. Each is topped with a circle, brass colored stopper that is the same on both. These vases pick up a variety of pale colors in their bodies and will complement any color of home decor.

The Crestview Collection Medium Ritz Covered Urn is made from glass that has been given a metallic finish from tarnished silver to rubbed bronze. The bulbous base is an elongated round with a bottle neck on top and crowned with a full circle. The coloration of this piece will blend with any home decor. You may want to consider pairing this urn with other display pieces that are taller and/or shorter to give a diverse look to your decor.

Product Title: large cobalt free style sculpture vase

Description: Experience artisinal elegance with the Crestview Collection Fairfield Vase. This sculpted free-form vase embodies refined craftsmanship and timeless beauty, making it the epitome of artisinal elegance. Perfect for adding a sophisticated touch to any room in your home.
